						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīrarājēndradēva. Year 20: A.D. 1226.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to register a gift of six <hi rend="italic">achchus</hi> by the <hi rend="italic">nagarattār</hi> of Muttūr to the temple of Kulōttuṅgachōḻichcharam Uḍaiyār for some services in the temple. Kuladīpa Bhaṭṭan, a <hi rend="italic">śiva-brāhmaṇa</hi> of the temple holding the right to temple service <hi rend="italic">(kāṇi)</hi> gave an undertaking to the <hi rend="italic">nagarattār</hi> to maintain the grant. (see Nos. 158, 159, 165)</p>						

						</summary>
